Crude Oil Futures Advance in New York, Reversing Earlier 3.9% Decline

-- B y   R i c h a r d   S t u b b e
-- 
2011-08-19T14:06:38Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-19/crude-falls-to-80-in-fourth-weekly-drop-brent-s-premium-reaches-record.html
Crude oil advanced in  New York ,
reversing an earlier decline of 3.9 percent. Crude for September
delivery rose 27 cents, or 0.3 percent, to $82.65 a barrel at
10:04 a.m. on the  New York Mercantile Exchange .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
